Police have arrested a 17-year-old pupil, for allegedly killing a seven-year-old grade one learner in Dikeledi Primary School, in Makapanstad in Moretele. It is alleged that the suspect attacked the victim inside the school toilets Wednesday morning. It is reported that the victim was stabbed with a sharp object in the neck and chest. Police spokesperson Tumelo Menyatso, says the victim died on his way to a local clinic. The suspect is expected to appear in the Moretele Magistrateâ€™s Court on Thursday on a charge of murder.   